{"title":"Officina Battaglin’s Made in Italy 1984 Frames are Limited to 12","link":"https://theradavist.com/officina-battaglins-1984-frame/","date":1734443241000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141109.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141109.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141109.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141109.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>Officina Battaglin just launched the 1984 (€3,800 frame), a <a href=\"https://officinabattaglin.com/products/limited-editions/1984-steel-road-frame/\" target=\"_blank\">limited-edition steel frame</a> that celebrates the 40th anniversary of Giovanni Battaglin’s retirement from professional cycling… </em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141152.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141152.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141152.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141152.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141140.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141140.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141140.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141140.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141126.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141126.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141126.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141126.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Only 12 frames will be crafted, each meticulously handbuilt in Italy by Officina Battaglin’s skilled craftsmen from Columbus HSS tubing and custom, oversized lugs. With a design inspired by Battaglin’s flagship <em>Portofino</em>, the 1984 is available exclusively with rim brakes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-2.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-2.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Geometry-Chart-Giovanni-Battaglin-1984-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>The 1984 can be built in 7 standard sizes or a custom geometry developed by Giovanni Battaglin himself.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141082.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141082.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141082.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141082.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141057.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141057.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141057.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/FF12-141057.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://officinabattaglin.com/products/limited-editions/1984-steel-road-frame/\" target=\"_blank\">Officina Battaglin</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/officina-battaglins-1984-frame/\">Officina Battaglin’s Made in Italy 1984 Frames are Limited to 12</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"12010836ca1302c1fb5ab9a6eac3487f79df9edbeeb25b2a80b6ebc825d7bdef","category":"Cycling"}